1 how to install sz/rz tool
yum install lrzsz

2 switch task to bg or fg
2.1 {cmd} &
2.2 jobs
2.3 fg {n}
2.4 bg {n}
2.5 kill {n}
2.6 ctrl + z

3 打包时排除指定目录
tar -czvf work.tar --exclude=test/1 test

4 alias
alias a='aa'

5 sudo
5.1 root login
5.2 chmod u+w /etc/sudoers
5.3 vim /etc/sudoers  
    xxx ALL=(ALL) 
5.4 chmod u-w /etc/sudoers
